+
+          **Request:** ${{ github.event.comment.body }}
+
+          <details>
+          <summary>üìä Diagnostic Output (click to expand)</summary>
+
+          \`\`\`
+          $DIAGNOSTICS
+          \`\`\`
+
+          </details>
+
+          ---
+          *If you need more specific information, reply with another @devops request.*"
+
